Installation of Libterrain
============================

  a) Prerequisites

In order to be compiled, Libterrain requires the packages listed below :

- autoconf
- automake
- libtool

It also requires the libnoise library which can be found here :

http://libnoise.sourceforge.net

There is also a fork of libnoise with a cmake build system available here :

http://github.com/qknight/libnoise

  b) Compilation and Installation instructions

To compile and install Libterrain, simply run the following commands :

./autogen.sh

./configure

make

make install

